title: Blazing 4 - Wild Card Weekend

description:
Colin doesn't do an official Blazing 5 for wild card weekend but he does go over all four games and which way he's leaning with RJ Bell of Fox Sports Radio and Pregame.com and RJ tells him which side the sharps in Vegas are on.
